makebread (0.3.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Import/export recipes (JSON, Markdown)
  * Print & PDF recipe cards
  * Timer presets per bread machine model
  * Ingredient scaling with baker's percentages
  * Swedish, German, French, Spanish translations
  * Bug fixes and UI improvements

